ComicInfo.Summary:
It’s time for The MAD 20 – The Dumbest People, Events and Things of 2015 – including Donald Trump, the Duggars, Hillary Clinton, the New England Patriots and more! Plus, general stupidity about selfie sticks,The Force Awakens, and Barbie! Plus, Planet Tad, Spy vs. Spy, the MAD Fold-In and even more dumb junk! So, vote with your dollars – elect to buy this issue today!
